---
title: Bison and Bacon Arrabbiata with Fresh Linguine
description: Arrabbiata literally means ‘angry’, which may sound puzzling given how tasty this pasta is! It's time to celebrate Canadian-raised bison with a luxurious arrabbiata! Earthy mushrooms, savoury garlic and fresh parsley fill out the background notes of this punchy pasta dish!
